This paper is about evaluating the contribution of different sentence encoder architectures on downstream language tasks. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV).
